### Get all availabilities
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctor-availabilities
Accept: application/json

### Create availability
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctor-availabilities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctor": { "id": 1 },
  "dayOfWeek": "MONDAY",
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "13:00:00"
}

### Get availability by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/doctor-availabilities/1
Accept: application/json

### Update availability
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/doctor-availabilities/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctor": { "id": 1 },
  "dayOfWeek": "TUESDAY",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "14:00:00"
}

### Delete availability
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/doctor-availabilities/1
